  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I just had gotten there when I got word that [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was to relieve C Company [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] because the First Battalion would resume the attack in the morning.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "My-- my battalion will not.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Well, I was a little unhappy about that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But I didn't relieve C Company until we started that night-- and late that-- well, in the early morning.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And by early morning, I had-- I didn't put I Company back in, I took one of my other companies, L Company, and put it in the can.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then I departed with what was left of the battalion.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Well, a short time after that, I got word that the 1st Battalion had run across another concentration camp, which it turned out was one of these slave labor camps.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It had about 8,000 people in it and they were in much better shape than the ones in Dachau, just a few miles from Dachau.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I was ordered to relieve the 1st Battalion so that they could continue the attack.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So I sent my K Company over to relive the 1st Battalion at that concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "That was on the 30th of April.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The morning we took-- the day we took the-- went-- first one into the camp was April 29, which was Sunday.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The following morning I-- I had resumed control of the camp with my L Company.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I send my K Company over to the new camp that the 1st Battalion had liberated and then I took what was left of the battalion, which was one company, I Company, and M Company, [INAUDIBLE] Company and had a headquarters into Munich and we established a command post.",
      "word_count": 49
    }
  ],
